	<description>
		<![CDATA[
			<p><b>JobBoard</b></p>
			
			<p>Version 1.5.1</p>
    <p>For this application to work properly, please ensure that you have configured the following settings:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Administrator email address</li>
        <li>Return email address</li>
    </ul>
    <p>You can configure these values by clicking on the "JobBoard" icon in the components menu. Then click on "Settings" to change the default values.</p>
